==[[w:Koine Greek|Koine Greek]]==

===Etymology===

From {{GG|1}} (as a negative particle) and [[βάρος]] {{GG|922}}; 

===Pronunciation===
ἀβαρής / abarēs / ab-ar-ace'

===Adjective===
'''ἀβαρής'''

# [[weightless]], that is (figuratively) not burdensome: - from being burdensome.

